SCREEN 6: AI SETUP DIALOG (AiSetupDialog)
==============================================================================

UI Design Grade:  B+
Feature Grade:    A-

LAYOUT & VISUAL HIERARCHY
  + Organized into clear grouped sections: AI Provider, Sorting Mode,
